OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBritish sign language gets 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclimate change update      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Deaf scientists and sign language      
OL,6, experts have created hundreds of new   
OL,7, signs for British Sign Language (BSL). 
OL,9,FExpanded BSL vocabulary now includes   
OL,10,Fclimate-related terms like "greenhouse 
OL,11,Fgas" and "carbon footprint", for which 
OL,12,Fthere were no official signs.          
OL,14,FThat meant children, teachers and      
OL,15,Fscientists would often have to         
OL,16,Ffinger-spell long, complex, scientific 
OL,17,Fterms.                                 
OL,19,F"We're trying to create the perfect    
OL,20,Fsigns that visualise scientific        
OL,21,Fconcepts," explains Dr Audrey Cameron. 
